name: Outsider - Houston graffiti zine
description:
Outsider is a Houston graffiti zine strictly focused on bombing. All the images in the zine were taken by me from 2005-2012. Artist such as Abels, DZ, Nekst, Sumoe, Verbs, Harsh to name a few are featured in this issue.



This issue is limited to 100 copies.
28 high-quality pages with full color spreads and b&w photos.
5.5 x 7 saddle stitched.

name: Original Mens vintage style collage white tshirt
description:
This is a one of a kind design that i had designed and printed. It is based off an original collage I have created. Only 25 shirts have been printed using a water base full color silk screen process. The water base process leaves the printed design feeling soft to the touch.

The shirts are printed on White Anvil 980 Pre-shrunk 4.5 oz 100% combed ring spun cotton.
Tubular construction with shoulder-to-shoulder tape. Double-needle sleeve and bottom hem.

The shirts run a little small, I would recommend getting one size larger. The size chart can be found here. http://www.anvilknitwear.com/content/view/popup/342



If you have any questions please feel free to contact me.

*The color in the design may vary from the final printed shirts.
